===Noun===
'''neuron''' (''plural'' '''neurons''')

# {{cytology}} A cell of the [[nervous system]], which conducts [[nerve impulse]]s; consisting of an [[axon]] and several [[dendrite]]s. Neurons are connected by [[synapse]]s.

